import styled from '@emotion/styled'
import { Paper } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'
import { WalletPreview } from '../Components/Components'

const LoginWrap = styled(Paper)(({ theme }) => ({
    borderRadius: 15,
    width: '100%',
    maxWidth: 600,
    height: 300,
    overflow: 'hidden',
    display: 'flex',
    alignItems: 'center',
    padding: 10
}))
export default function Login() {
    return (
        <LoginWrap elevation={24}>
            <WalletPreview />
        </LoginWrap>
    )
}
